%% Message Lifecycle
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Sent: sendMessage()
    Sent --> Anchored: Coordinator anchors hash
    Anchored --> Claimable: Hash verified on destination
    Claimable --> Claimed: claimMessage()
    Claimed --> [*]: Executed

    note right of Sent
        L1: MessageSent event emitted
        L2: MessageSent event + rolling hash
    end note

    note right of Anchored
        L1→L2: Coordinator anchors on L2
        L2→L1: Included in finalization
    end note

    note right of Claimable
        Proof available
        Can be claimed by user or Postman
    end note
